teacheasy.test

Class Iteration3XMLTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.test.Iteration3XMLTest

  • public class Iteration3XMLTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to test the XML Parser and writer and check that errors/warnings are added to the appropriate lists under different circumstances

    1.0 24 May 2015
    Author:
